Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一大包怎麼回事啊  裝了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這池子好像很深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水藻也很多  掉下去會淹死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人？哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了  掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  啥都沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看錯了  走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人回答啊  出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到得比預定時間早
