Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  我們隨便就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水池  這裡的院子裡也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然  這片土地流傳著人魚的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都有水池和沼澤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老師你會裝在包裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目家的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想著怎麼會這麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷渡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…你這…
